            <note xml:id="foot.f2">The enclosure has not been found, but see <hi rend="italic">Midland Naturalist</hi> 1 (1878): 1–4 for the account of the formation of the Midland Union of Natural History Societies.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3"><ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_5261.xml">Thomas Wright</ref>.</note>
